{"tid":1832536,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"穆迪將港鐵公司(00066.HK)評級降至Aa3級","createTime":"2020-01-21T08:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T12:32:37.000Z","uid":95138,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d5f588c0057bc3d2bea44d2180fb0e2ada5049","tid":1832536,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"評級機構穆迪公布，將港鐵公司(<a href=\"http://00066.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00066.HK&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6q%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=a5871163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00066.HK</a>)評級由Aa2級降至Aa3級，評級展望由「負面」轉為「穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n該行指出下調港鐵評級主要因為該行將香港的評級由Aa2級降至Aa3級，認為香港評級下調對與政府相關的發行商之信貸質素有負面影響，加上在穆迪的違約分析中，政府所提供的支持、其評級及信貸質素在機構的評級上扮演重要角色，而港鐵對香港政府評級及評級展望轉變亦較敏感，認為港鐵對港府依賴較高，在營運及財務上亦有較緊密關聯。<br />\n<br />\n而在環境、社會及管治因素上，港鐵的評級反映面對溫和社會風險，主要考慮在香港社會不穩及沙中線工程項目上如何確保營運安全，公司同時亦面對工程項目上的管治風險。(el/u)"},{"pid":"f6e6511001dd3a25d2e69fc84bccbf5510f260f6","tid":1832536,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"Source: AASTOCKS"},{"pid":"eeb84a4175917cb100366bf78cad4e67428e228b","tid":1832536,"uid":194298,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"穆迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />火力全開"},{"pid":"452225e9f0beeef070af432ebd54313a7617e382","tid":1832536,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"又幫沙中線投不信任票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f342b177071dfea6dee40f1fd85d12991dccb95","tid":1832536,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb84a4175917cb100366bf78cad4e67428e228b","tid":1832536,"uid":194298,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"穆迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n